    "In our study of digital virtual humans, we focused on investigating methods of generating 3D avatars, which can reduce the cost in the Metaverse of generating digital bodies.",
    "In addition, we reviewed fashion learning and analysis methods that could assist both fashion designers and consumers in the Metaverse.",
    "We also envisioned certain fashion scenarios in the Metaverse and discussed several important open issues associated with the future development of the Metaverse.",
    "We believe this survey will be instructive for both academics and industrial practitioners, and will shed some light on the study of fashion tasks in the Metaverse."
